00w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/mick-fleetwood-john-mayall@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/mick-fleetwood-john-mayall@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/mick-fleetwood-john-mayall@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/mick-fleetwood-john-mayall@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mick-fleetwood">米克·弗利特伍德</a>向已故英国蓝调先驱约翰·梅奥尔致敬——看看弗利特伍德下面怎么说。</p><p>昨天（7 月 24 日），有消息称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/british-blues-pioneer-john-mayall-has-died-aged-90-3777318">Mayall 去世，享年 90 岁</a>，就在他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rock-roll-hall-of-fame-2024-ozzy-osbourne-cher-and-more-to-be-inducted-3749163">即将入选摇滚名人堂</a>前不久。在他漫长而辉煌的职业生涯中，梅奥尔通过他的乐队 Blues Breakers 为许多年轻音乐家提供了一个平台，如弗利特伍德、约翰·麦克维、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eric-clapton">埃里克·克莱普顿</a>等。 </p><figure id="attachment_3777319" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3777319" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3777319" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/john-mayall@2000x1270.jpg" alt="1982 年 6 月 13 日，约翰·梅奥尔 (John Mayall) 在伊利诺伊州芝加哥公园西区的舞台上表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/john-mayall@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/john-mayall@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/john-mayall@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/john-mayall@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/john-mayall@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/john-mayall@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3777319" class="wp-caption-text">约翰·梅奥尔.图片来源：Paul Natkin/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>梅奥尔去世后，米克·弗利特伍德分享了一篇帖子，纪念并缅怀他已故的音乐合作者。弗利特伍德在 Instagram 上写道：“约翰·梅奥尔去世的消息……在很多方面都让我感到失去了一位音乐之父！约翰·梅奥尔是我们许多年轻英国球员的指路明灯！”</p><p>他还称赞 Mayall 间接创建了 Fleetwood Mac：“作为‘Blues Breakers’乐队的一员，我们三个人——Peter Green、John McVie 和我自己在 1967 年组建了 Fleetwood Mac！音乐界的许多人都非常感谢他。”</p><p>请参阅下面的完整帖子。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C90IfHbSTys/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 55