/film/benedict-cumberbatch-to-play-pete-seeger-in-bob-dylan-biopic-3445761">本来是由本尼迪克特·康伯巴奇扮演的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/benedict-cumberbatch">。</a>据<a href="https://deadline.com/2024/01/edward-norton-pete-seeger-bob-dylan-a-complete-unknown-1235804813/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>好莱坞截止日期</em></a>报道，康伯巴奇因日程安排冲突而退出了该项目。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/edward-norton-replace-benedict-cumberbatch-pete-seeger-bob-dylan-biopic-3577346">爱德华·诺顿随后被任命扮演西格。</a></p><p>柴勒梅德<a href="https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/timothee-chalamet-bob-dylan-trailer-b2585150.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">于 2020 年</a>被宣布将饰演鲍勃·迪伦，但曼高德证实<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/timothee-chalamet-says-hes-heard-12-hours-worth-of-unreleased-bob-dylan-songs-3562977">柴勒梅德将在<em>《完全未知》</em>中演唱</a>，这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/little-women-film-review-2590169"><em>《小妇人》</em></a>演员曾在<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/wonka">《旺卡》</a>中展示了他的声乐能力。</em></p><p>去年，这位演员表示，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/timothee-chalamet-says-hes-heard-12-hours-worth-of-unreleased-bob-dylan-songs-3562977">听过大量未发行的鲍勃·迪伦音乐，</a>为扮演这位标志性艺术家做准备。作为在传记片中饰演鲍勃·迪伦的训练的一部分，查拉梅德与<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/timothee-chalamet-training-to-play-bob-dylan-austin-butlers-elvis-team-3516576">协助奥斯汀·巴特勒出演《猫王》的团队</a>合作<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/elvis-review-3249220"><em>。</em></a></p><p>在最近与<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/dune-part-2"><em>《沙丘：第二部分》</em></a>联合主演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/austin-butler">巴特勒</a>一起接受<em><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o6ldsJzCFnE&amp;ab_channel=NME" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NME</a></em>采访时，柴勒梅德表示，他希望<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/timothee-chalamet-wants-austin-butlers-elvis-to-be-in-his-bob-dylan-biopic-3597072">巴特勒版的埃尔维斯·普雷斯利</a>出现在<em>《完全未知》</em>中。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="奥斯汀·巴特勒和蒂莫西·柴勒梅德：成为猫王和鲍勃·迪伦" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtub